claim.claim-text:
1. An airbag device for a flying object, which protects at least one of objects to be protected mounted on the flying object, the airbag device comprising:
an airbag which is provided adjacent to at least one of the objects to be protected mounted on the flying object, said airbag is selectively shifted between a folded position and a deployed position, such that in the deployed position the airbag covers at least a portion of the periphery of the object to be protected mounted on the flying object;
at least one vent hole capable of discharging gas inside the airbag, and for intake of air when internal pressure inside the airbag is negative;
a gas generator which is connected to the airbag and is capable of supplying gas into the airbag to inflate the airbag when the gas generator is activated;
wherein said vent hole is disposed on a foldable portion of the airbag, such that in said folded position said vent hole is blocked, and in said deployed position said vent holes is exposed allowing air intake.
